Privacy Policy
06th March 2017
This policy applies to all information collected or submitted on Optimise, 
      Transcibe, Fluency Calculator website and our apps for iPhone and any other devices and platforms.
History of Changes
March 06, 2017: First published.
August 13, 2019: Removed some analytics.
Information we collect
Our product occasionally collects analytics through google analytics.
      Things like device type are stored.
If you enable 'share with developers' when you set up your phone,
      information regarding our products will be shared with Apple
      which we will have access to (e.g. Crash Reports).
Information usage
We use the information we can access through Apple
      to operate and improve our website, apps, and customer support.
We do not share your personal information with outside parties
      except to the extent necessary to accomplish functionality.
In the future we may sell to, buy, merge with, or partner with other businesses.
      In such transactions user information may be among the transferred assets.
Security
We do not have copies of your files.
      We take no responsibility for lost,
        damaged or corrupted files and we strongly recommend you use a backup system or service.
Your Consent
By using our site and products you consent to our privacy policy.
Contacting Us
If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy, you may email privacy@joyventures.xyz
Changes to this policy
If we decide to change our privacy policy we will post
      those changes on this page and update the privacy policy modification date above.